"title": "8722: doubt, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8722",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Doubt leads to insecurity and lack of trust concerning God's willingness and ability to deliver his people. It also leads to a fear of people and situations.</p>\n<h2>Doubting God's truth</h2>\n<h3>Doubt as a questioning of God's words</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1\">GEN 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:4\">GEN 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:19\">ISA 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:15\">JER 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:4\">2PE 3:4</a></p>\n<h3>Doubt as lack of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:21-Matt21:22\">MAT 21:21–21:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:23-Mark11:24\">MRK 11:23–11:24</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">MAT 17:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:6\">MRK 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:14\">MRK 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:6\">LUK 17:6</a></p>\n<h3>Doubt as wavering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6\">JAS 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:21\">1KI 18:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:20\">ROM 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13-Eph4:14\">EPH 4:13–4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Doubt as double-mindedness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:8\">JAS 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:40-2Kgs17:41\">2KI 17:40–17:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:21\">1CO 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a></p>\n<h2>Doubt as insecurity about relationship with God</h2>\n<h3>Doubting God's compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:7-Ps77:9\">PSA 77:7–77:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:13\">PSA 90:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:6\">HEB 12:5–12:6</a></p>\n<h3>Doubting God's concern</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:20\">JOB 30:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:14\">ISA 49:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:1-Ps13:2\">PSA 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1-Ps22:2\">PSA 22:1–22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:17\">PSA 35:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:27\">ISA 40:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:18-Jer8:22\">JER 8:18–8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:8\">LAM 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:2\">HAB 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>Doubting God's desire to deliver</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer45:3\">JER 45:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:22-Exod5:23\">EXO 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:1-Lam2:9\">LAM 2:1–2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:13-Lam3:20\">LAM 3:13–3:20</a></p>\n<h3>Doubting God's ability to deliver</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:18-Ps78:22\">PSA 78:18–78:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:10-Exod14:12\">EXO 14:10–14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:41-Ps78:43\">PSA 78:41–78:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39-Mark4:40\">MRK 4:39–4:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:24–8:25</a></p>\n<h3>Doubting God's justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:1\">JER 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:23\">JOB 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:13-Ps73:16\">PSA 73:13–73:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:2\">PSA 82:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16-Jer15:18\">JER 15:16–15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:13\">HAB 1:13</a></p>\n<h2>Doubt as fear of people and situations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:30-Matt14:31\">MAT 14:30–14:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:12-Gen12:13\">GEN 12:12–12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:30\">GEN 19:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:7\">GEN 26:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:5\">JOS 7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:11\">1SA 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:12-Isa51:13\">ISA 51:12–51:13</a></p>",
